--- !u!114 &4166184519406471652
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 5446361219511307707}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: f4688fdb7df04437aeb418b961361dc5, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  m_Material: {fileID: 0}
  m_Color: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
  m_RaycastTarget: 1
  m_RaycastPadding: {x: 0, y: 0, z: 0, w: 0}
  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: '<color=#425375><b>Atk (Attack Power)</b></color>

    - Represents the
    strength of your physical attacks.

    - Shows the damage range of a regular
    melee attack, before resistances.


    <color=#425375><b>MAtk (Magic Attack
    Power)</b></color>

    - Represents the strength of your magical attacks.

    -
    Shows the damage range of a 100% magic damage skill, before resistances.


    <color=#425375><b>Hit
    (Accuracy)</b></color>

    - Represents your ability to land physical attacks.

    -
    Compared against the target''s flee to determine hit or miss.

    - Magic attacks
    always land and ignore hit.


    <color=#425375><b>Crit (Critical)</b></color>

    -
    Represents your chance to land critical attacks.

    - Criticals are guaranteed
    hits that bypass defense.

    - Criticals deal your maximum possible damage.

    -
    Most skills and magic attacks cannot crit.


    <color=#425375><b>Def (Defense)</b></color>

    -
    Represents your resistance to physical attacks.

    - Hard defense (first value)
    cuts incoming physical damage by a percent.

    - Soft defense (second value)
    reduces physical damage by a fixed amount.


    <color=#425375><b>MDef (Magic
    Defense)</b></color>

    - Represents your resistance to magical attacks.

    -
    Hard defense (first value) cuts incoming magical damage by a percent.

    -
    Soft defense (second value) reduces magical damage by a fixed amount.


    <color=#425375><b>Flee
    (Evasion)</b></color>

    - Represents your ability to dodge physical attacks.

    -
    Compared against the attacker''s hit to determine dodge chance.

    - Reduced
    when attacked by multiple enemies at once.

    - Ineffective against most magical
    attacks.


    <color=#425375><b>Aspd (Attack Speed)</b></color>

    - Represents
    how many attack actions you can perform per second.

    - Limits all attack
    actions, including skills and magical attacks.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: f526b3b4777a17244865df0c27c65fbf, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 2100000, guid: 73cb0a841b5900148a63e4f50e32e931, type: 2}
