  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: '<color=#425375><b>Str (Strength)</b></color>

    - Increases physical
    damage with melee weapons, becoming stronger with higher levels of strength.

    -
    Increases weight capacity.


    <color=#425375><b>Agi (Agility)</b></color>

    -
    Increases your evasion rate (flee).

    - Increases attack speed and the rate
    at which you can execute skills.


    <color=#425375><b>Vit (Vitality)</b></color>

    -
    Increases your max HP and HP recovery rate.

    - Reduces incoming physical
    damage by a flat amount.

    - Adds resistance to physical status effects.


    <color=#425375><b>Int
    (Intelligence)</b></color>

    - Increases magical damage, becoming stronger
    with higher levels of intelligence.

    - Increases your max SP and SP recovery
    rate.

    - Reduces incoming magical damage by a flat amount.

    - Adds resistance
    to magical status effects.


    <color=#425375><b>Dex (Dexterity)</b></color>

    -
    Increases physical damage with bows, becoming stronger with higher levels of
    dexterity.

    - Increases your physical accuracy rate (hit).

    - Improves
    casting speed.


    <color=#425375><b>Luk (Luck)</b></color>

    - Increases
    your critical chance.

    - Increases likeliness that random chance events in
    combat will favor you over your opponent.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: f526b3b4777a17244865df0c27c65fbf, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 2100000, guid: 73cb0a841b5900148a63e4f50e32e931, type: 2}
